[
  {
    "content_id": 796830,
    "reference_id": 12215,
    "title": "哈該書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這段開場陳述（<span><em>開頭的概述，</em></span><em>superscription</em>）確定了作者、聽眾、日期，以及<span>促使先知發預言的背景</span>。</p><ul><li><p>第二年：大流士一世（<span>赫斯他皮西，</span>Hystaspes）於波斯帝國（公元前539至331年）早期，也就是公元前521至486年統治波斯。哈該的信息是舊約聖經中日期最精確的預言之一。</p></li><li><p>先知（希伯來文為nabi’）一詞表明哈該是神的代表，<span>奉差遣以神的權柄說話</span>。</p></li><li><p>所羅巴伯帶領一批希伯來人<span>自巴比倫被擄之地歸回巴勒斯坦（</span>Palestine<span>）</span>，<span>並在哈該服事期間擔任波斯任命的猶大省省長</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:1-Ezra2:2\">拉2:1–2</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:2\">3:2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:7\">尼7:7</a>）。</p></li><li><p>約書亞當時是大祭司。在他的監督下，祭壇得以重建，第二聖殿被奉獻（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:2\">拉3:2</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:2\">5:2</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:15\">6:15</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:1",
          "end_ref": "37001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796825,
    "reference_id": 12210,
    "title": "哈該書 1:1–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001001-37001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>第一條信息呼籲耶路撒冷的百姓專注於恢復對神的正確敬拜。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:1",
          "end_ref": "37001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796831,
    "reference_id": 12216,
    "title": "哈該書 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>萬軍之耶和華：這是哈該和<span>撒迦利亞</span>最<span>常用來稱呼神的表達方式</span>，其強調了神話語背後無比的力量。<span>耶和華能隨時差遣無數天上的軍隊來成就祂的旨意</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:17\">王下6:17</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:53\">太26:53</a>）。這樣的思想旨在鼓舞那些感到無助而渺小的猶大人。</p></li><li><p>時候尚未來到：由於乾旱和瘟疫導致的農作物歉收，<span>嚴重削弱了猶大的經濟</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:6\">該1:6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:9-Hag1:11\">9–11</a>），因此，百姓便以為自己無力重建聖殿。然而哈該<span>卻使他們明白</span>，他們<span>不能任由聖殿荒涼</span>，因為若不重建耶和華的殿，神就不會賜福或復興他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:4\">1:4</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:7-Hag1:8\">7–8</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:2",
          "end_ref": "37001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796832,
    "reference_id": 12217,
    "title": "哈該書 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>你們自己還......？<span>在先知文學中，</span>修辭性問句<span>的作用不是要對方回答問題，而是要引發聽眾的認同</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:3\">2:3</a>）。<span>這樣的提問旨在堵住聽眾可能為自己找藉口的機會，使他們無法為拒絕信息而辯解。</span></p></li><li><p>百姓居住的華麗（或被遮蓋<em>的</em><span>、<em>鑲板的</em>）的房屋，與神的聖殿形成了鮮明對比——聖殿當時是一片廢墟（或荒廢），因此無法使用。</span></p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:4",
          "end_ref": "37001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796833,
    "reference_id": 12218,
    "title": "哈該書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>看看發生在你身上的事情（字面意思為<em>將你的心放在這些事情上</em>；<em>和合本譯為：</em>你們要省察自己的行為）：對於希伯來人而言，<em>心</em>是思考、感受和使用意志的地方。因此，這個命令（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:7\">1:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:15\">2:15</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:18\">18</a>）呼籲百姓仔細思考，並得出正確的結論——要看清他們所遭遇的事（乾旱和貧困，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:6\">1:6</a>），與他們未能恢復對耶和華的正確敬拜（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:8-Hag1:9\">1:8–9</a>）之間的關係。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:5",
          "end_ref": "37001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796834,
    "reference_id": 12219,
    "title": "哈該書 1:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>吃......喝......穿衣服：<span>每個動詞都表達了持續性的動作（即，你們不斷地往盤子裡加食物……不斷地喝啊喝……一層又一層地穿上衣服），加深了徒勞無功之感。</span></p></li><li><p>破漏的囊（字面意思為<em>一個被刺開的袋子</em>）：這個意象描繪了工價的損失。許多家庭儘管辛勤勞作，但仍面臨貧困。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:6",
          "end_ref": "37001006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796835,
    "reference_id": 12220,
    "title": "哈該書 1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>要上山：耶路撒冷周圍的樹木不足以滿足聖殿工程的需求。這些材料很可能需要從北方的黎巴嫩和敘利亞進口。</p></li><li><p>重建我的殿的呼召，強調了敬拜在群體生命中的重要性，以及必須有合乎律法的敬拜場所，才能按著神的律法敬拜耶和華。當耶和華的聖殿——祂的居所——被重建時，這片土地將會經歷祝福與興旺（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:4\">2:4</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:8",
          "end_ref": "37001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796836,
    "reference_id": 12221,
    "title": "哈該書 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>我就吹去：因為百姓們生命的優先次序錯誤——他們只想到自己，卻沒有想到神，所以耶和華摧毀了他們的收成。</p></li><li><p>這是萬軍之耶和華說的：這個「神是說話者的公式（God-as-speaker formula）」，<span>常常作為預言的結尾</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:13\">1:13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:8\">2:8</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:17\">17</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:23\">23</a>），<span>證實了哈該的信息是神確實的話語</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:9",
          "end_ref": "37001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796826,
    "reference_id": 12211,
    "title": "哈該書 1:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>我命乾旱臨到：<span>百姓沒有認出自己所遭遇的困境，其實是神對他們錯置生命優先次序的審判。因此，哈該便按照聖約中所附的咒詛來解釋當前的景況</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15-Deut28:68\">申28:15–68</a>，特別是<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:22-Deut28:24\">22至24</a>節、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:38-Deut28:40\">38–40</a>節）。</p></li><li><p>乾旱（希伯來文為khoreb）一詞是對應到「荒涼」（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:4\">該1:4</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:9\">9</a>；希伯來文為khareb）一詞的文字遊戲。<span>猶大人所經歷的，正好與他們使耶和華的殿處於荒廢狀態的情況相吻合</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:11",
          "end_ref": "37001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796827,
    "reference_id": 12212,
    "title": "哈該書 1:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>剩下的百姓指的是從巴比倫歸回的人。他們全部團結一致，參與重建工程。</p></li><li><p>百姓也在耶和華面前存敬畏的心：他們以敬畏和崇拜來回應神，<span>並重新調整了生命的優先次序，把屬靈的價值放在物質的豐富之前。</span></p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:12",
          "end_ref": "37001012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796828,
    "reference_id": 12213,
    "title": "哈該書 1:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>哈該被稱為耶和華的使者<span>（這個希伯來片語在其它地方常被譯為「耶和華的<em>天使</em></span>〔<em>angel of the</em> Lord〕<span>」），這獨特的稱呼賦予哈該一種特殊的權柄，表明他是耶和華的代表。</span></p></li><li><p>我與你們同在：這句話確認了神與猶大百姓所立的約，表明了祂親自的臨在，同時也是對<span>聖殿重建工作的支持。</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:4-Hag2:5\">2:4–5</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:3\">創26:3</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:12\">出3:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">賽41:10</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:5\">43:5</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:11\">耶30:11</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:13",
          "end_ref": "37001013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796829,
    "reference_id": 12214,
    "title": "哈該書 1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華激動（字面意思為<em>攪動靈</em>）百姓的心來成就祂的旨意（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1\">拉1:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:17\">賽13:17</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:25\">41:25</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:1\">耶51:1</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:11\">11</a>）。對神真正的敬拜促使神的子民甘願奉獻服事神。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:14",
          "end_ref": "37001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796847,
    "reference_id": 12232,
    "title": "哈該書 2:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在同年的十月十七日（和合本譯為：七月二十一日）：這是住棚節的最後一天，<span>一個慶祝夏季收穫的節期</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:34-Lev23:43\">利23:34–43</a>）。<span>幾百年前，</span>所羅門的聖殿<span>正是在這個節期中被獻上的</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:2\">王上8:2</a>）。哈該的信息正好在此時宣講，<span>為百姓在當前的困境與沮喪中帶來</span>盼望與勸勉。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:1",
          "end_ref": "37002001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796837,
    "reference_id": 12222,
    "title": "哈該書 2:1–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002001-37002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>哈該的第二條信息是向群體保證，神沒有忘記祂透過早期先知所應許的，要賜福並恢復他們（例：<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:1-Isa35:10\">賽35章</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:1-Isa40:11\">40:1–11</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:1-Isa52:12\">52:1–12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:36-Jer32:44\">耶32:36–44</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6-Jer33:26\">33:6–26</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:1",
          "end_ref": "37002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796852,
    "reference_id": 12237,
    "title": "哈該書 2:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>從前的榮耀屬於所羅門的聖殿（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:38\">王上6:38</a>），<span>猶大的一些年長者在年輕時、被擄到巴比倫之前曾親眼見過</span>。<span>他們在看到新殿的根基被立下時就放聲哭泣</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:12-Ezra3:13\">拉3:12–13</a>），因為這與從前相比之下，真的微不足道。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:3",
          "end_ref": "37002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796853,
    "reference_id": 12238,
    "title": "哈該書 2:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>雖然......當剛強：這表示著語氣從責備與挑戰，轉為勉勵與肯定（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:6-Josh1:7\">書1:6–7</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
