  {
    "content_id": 796855,
    "reference_id": 12240,
    "title": "哈該書 2:6–7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002006-37002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>神會在即將到來的審判之日，再一次震動天地</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:19-Isa2:21\">賽2:19–21，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:28\">30:28</a>）。<span>先前的震動，是指出埃及時對埃及的審判</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:21-Hag2:22\">該2:21–22</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:31\">出14:31</a>）。<span>新約聖經則將再過不多時與耶穌基督的再來聯繫起來</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:26-Heb12:27\">來12:26–27</a>）。<span>哈該可能在他之後將要發生的事件中，看見了神最終審判的預兆。</span>（例：波斯被希臘征服，希臘被羅馬征服。見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:39-Dan2:45\">但2:39–45</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:6",
          "end_ref": "37002007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796856,
    "reference_id": 12241,
    "title": "哈該書 2:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>珍寶……必都運來聖殿，作為對以色列之神的奉獻與敬拜。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:7",
          "end_ref": "37002007",
