    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796857,
    "reference_id": 12242,
    "title": "哈該書 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>後來的榮耀：或許<span>哈該心中所想的是彌賽亞要來到祂的殿</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:1\">瑪3:1</a>）。耶穌在嬰兒時期被帶到耶和華的殿中（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:22\">路2:22</a>），並且成年後在那裡教導（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:45-Luke19:47\">路19:45–47</a>）。耶穌——<span>這位成了肉身的神的道——比聖殿更大</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:6\">太12:6</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:13-John2:22\">約2:13–22</a>）。雖然只有少數人認識到，但耶穌在聖殿中的同在，遠勝過摩西時期會幕中的榮耀以及所羅門聖殿的榮耀（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:29-Luke2:32\">路2:29–32</a>）。</p></li><li><p>在這地方我必賜平安：祭司的祝禱（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:24-Num6:26\">民6:24–26</a>）是聖殿禮拜儀式的一部分。在末後的日子，神將與以色列立平安的約（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:25\">結34:25</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:26\">37:26</a>）。重建聖殿所帶來的美好結果，是對未來的<em>平安</em>的保證。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:9",
          "end_ref": "37002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796838,
    "reference_id": 12223,
    "title": "哈該書 2:10–19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002010-37002019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>第三條信息的主題，是律法對</span>禮儀上的潔淨<span>的教導。這些教導仍然有效。神盼望祂的子民聖潔，因為祂自己是聖潔的</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44-Lev11:45\">利11:44–45</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:10",
          "end_ref": "37002019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796839,
    "reference_id": 12224,
    "title": "哈該書 2:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>向祭司問：祭司的職責是教導和解釋律法（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:10\">申33:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:7-Mal2:9\">瑪2:7–9</a>），<span>因此，有關禮儀上的潔淨的信息是針對他們而說的</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:11",
          "end_ref": "37002011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796840,
    "reference_id": 12225,
    "title": "哈該書 2:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>便算為聖嗎？這個問題指的是來自聖祭的肉，以及<span>禮儀上的潔淨</span>和不潔淨如何傳遞（見「<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203122\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesThemes\">潔淨、不潔淨與聖潔</span>」主題註釋）。攜帶聖肉——<span>即為獻祭而分別出來並預備好的肉</span>——會使人的袍子成為聖潔（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:18\">利6:18</a>）。然而，這聖潔無法傳遞給第三件物品。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:12",
          "end_ref": "37002012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 203122,
          "content_id": 700185,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotesThemes",
          "label": "潔淨、不潔淨與聖潔",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796841,
    "reference_id": 12226,
    "title": "哈該書 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>禮儀上的不潔遠比禮儀上的潔淨更容易傳播。凡觸摸屍體的人就會被玷污，因而成為不潔。凡是被</span>儀式<span>上不潔之人所觸碰的東西，也都會變得不潔</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:11-Num19:13\">民19:11–13</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:22\">22</a>）。哈該在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:14\">哈該書二章14節</a>中應用了這一點。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:13",
          "end_ref": "37002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796842,
    "reference_id": 12227,
    "title": "哈該書 2:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這民......也是如此：<span>單單從被擄之地回到神所應許以色列的地，並不能使猶大百姓成為聖潔。他們仍然是不潔的，因為他們沒有遵行神與他們所立之約的訓誨。他們的工作，甚至他們的敬拜，都被不潔所玷污；耶和華的殿的廢墟象徵著百姓的悖逆。重建聖殿是一個具體的標誌，表明人心已經改變，並且重新遵行與神所立之約。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:14",
          "end_ref": "37002014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796843,
    "reference_id": 12228,
    "title": "哈該書 2:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>要追想（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"12218\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">1:5的研讀註釋</span>）：<span>神的賜福，無論是屬靈的或物質的，都取決於神子民的順服</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:6-Deut30:10\">申30:6–10</a>）。<span>哈該呼籲百姓持續自我省察，好進行悔改；並且要持守敬畏耶和華的心，這正是他第一個信息所要教導的</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:7\">該1:7</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:12\">12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:15",
          "end_ref": "37002015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 12218,
          "content_id": 796833,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "哈該書 1:5",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796844,
    "reference_id": 12229,
    "title": "哈該書 2:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "37002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>回轉（和合本譯為：歸向）通常是代表悔改。</p></li><li><p>你們仍不：希伯來人從摩西時代起（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:27\">申31:27</a>）直到耶穌時代（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:17\">太17:17</a>），都一直是頑梗與悖逆的。</p></li><li><p>旱風、霉爛：<span>這些災禍是因不順服神的約而臨到的</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:22\">申28:22</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "37002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:17",
          "end_ref": "37002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAG 2:17"
        }
      ],
